    </children>
  </item>
  <item nodeId="node-29">
    <command xml:space="preserve">west</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">Engine Room&#x000A;Massive turbines roar around you. Your people's bio-energy is being drained to power this machine. You feel their pain.&#x000A;&#x000A;You can see a control panel here.&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
