  <item nodeId="node-407">
    <command xml:space="preserve">look map</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">============================================================&#x000A;&#x000A;               WORLD MAP: THE GHANRION FOREST               &#x000A;&#x000A;============================================================&#x000A;&#x000A;&#x000A;&#x000A;      &lt;Ghanrion Camp&gt;  GHANRION CAMP&#x000A;&#x000A;             |&#x000A;&#x000A;           NORTH&#x000A;&#x000A;             | (blocked until Xilar is freed)&#x000A;&#x000A;             |&#x000A;&#x000A;(Human Crash) -- WEST -- (Observation) -- EAST -- (Bioluminescent) -- EAST -- (Ravine)&#x000A;&#x000A;(Crash Site )            (   Rock    )            (    Forest    )            &#x000A;&#x000A;                                                                                |&#x000A;&#x000A;                                                                              DOWN&#x000A;&#x000A;                                                                                |&#x000A;&#x000A;                                                                      (Underground Tunnels)&#x000A;&#x000A;&#x000A;&#x000A;--- LOCATION GUIDE ---&#x000A;&#x000A;&#x000A;&#x000A;BIOLUMINESCENT FOREST  &lt;-- YOU ARE HERE&#x000A;&#x000A;  The central hub of the map. Your starting location and the heart&#x000A;&#x000A;  of the Ghanrion world. NPC: Zarb (young Ghanrion scout).&#x000A;&#x000A;  Exits: EAST (Ravine), WEST (Observation Rock), NORTH (Ghanrion Camp)&#x000A;&#x000A;&#x000A;&#x000A;THE RAVINE&#x000A;&#x000A;  East of the Bioluminescent Forest. A deep rocky ravine.&#x000A;&#x000A;  NPC: Xilar (trapped Ghanrion warrior). Key action: HELP XILAR.&#x000A;&#x000A;  Exits: WEST (Bioluminescent Forest), DOWN (Underground Tunnels)&#x000A;&#x000A;&#x000A;&#x000A;UNDERGROUND TUNNELS&#x000A;&#x000A;  Beneath the Ravine. Dark passages lit by bioluminescent plants.&#x000A;&#x000A;  A hidden escape route used in the final sequence.&#x000A;&#x000A;  Exits: UP (The Ravine)&#x000A;&#x000A;&#x000A;&#x000A;OBSERVATION ROCK&#x000A;&#x000A;  West of the Bioluminescent Forest. A high vantage point.&#x000A;&#x000A;  The smoke of the crash site is visible from here.&#x000A;&#x000A;  Exits: EAST (Bioluminescent Forest), WEST (Human Crash Site -- DANGEROUS)&#x000A;&#x000A;&#x000A;&#x000A;HUMAN CRASH SITE&#x000A;&#x000A;  West of Observation Rock. A burning crash site with armed human soldiers.&#x000A;&#x000A;  WARNING: Entering without Xilar's help ends the game. NPC: Captain Jack.&#x000A;&#x000A;  Exits: EAST (Observation Rock)&#x000A;&#x000A;&#x000A;&#x000A;GHANRION CAMP&#x000A;&#x000A;  North of the Bioluminescent Forest. The final destination.&#x000A;&#x000A;  LOCKED until you free Xilar in the Ravine. NPC: Vael (elder).&#x000A;&#x000A;  Warning: Arriving triggers the Camp Siege finale.&#x000A;&#x000A;  Exits: SOUTH (Bioluminescent Forest)&#x000A;&#x000A;&#x000A;&#x000A;--- RECOMMENDED PATH ---&#x000A;&#x000A;  1. Talk to Zarb (Bioluminescent Forest)&#x000A;&#x000A;  2. Go EAST -- Ravine -- free Xilar (HELP XILAR)&#x000A;&#x000A;  3. Explore freely. Try USE TELEPATHY&#x000A;&#x000A;  4. Go WEST then WEST -- visit Observation Rock and the Crash Site&#x000A;&#x000A;  5. Return and go NORTH -- Ghanrion Camp -- face the finale&#x000A;&#x000A;&#x000A;&#x000A;============================================================&#x000A;&gt;</result>
    <commentary xml:space="preserve"></commentary>
    <changed>NO</changed>
  </item>
