  <item nodeId="node-251">
    <command xml:space="preserve">w</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">You move toward the open ridge, but before you can step into the light, Xilar's hand closes firmly around your arm.&#x000A;&#x000A;"Not yet. They are still searching the crash site. If they see us now, they will follow us straight back to the camp."&#x000A;&#x000A;He draws you back into the shadow of the rocks. You return to the Observation Rock.&#x000A;&#x000A;[Your score has just gone up by three points.]&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
    <commentary xml:space="preserve"></commentary>
    <changed>NO</changed>
    <children>
